title: Szilvia Szeitl
text: Szilvia Szeitl (born 26 April 1987 in <a href="Budapest">Budapest</a>) is a <a href="Hungary">Hungarian</a> <a href="women%27s%20soccer">football</a> <a href="defender%20%28association%20football%29">defender</a> currently playing in the <a href="Noi%20NB%20I">Hungarian First Division</a> for <a href="1.%20FC%20Femina">1. FC Femina</a>, with whom she has also played the <a href="UEFA%20Women%27s%20Champions%20League">Champions League</a>. She is a member of the <a href="Hungary%20women%27s%20national%20football%20team">Hungarian national team</a>.
